OL,3,CDrug feuds at house days before woman
OL,4,Cshot dead, court hears
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, a jury heard evidence from
OL,7,FKatie Summers, who owned the flat
OL,8,Fwhere the shooting took place. She
OL,9,Fsaid Marcus Huntley and a friend had
OL,10,Fmoved in to sell that crack cocaine
OL,11,Ffrom her flat in Talbot Green in the
OL,12,Fweeks before the shooting.
OL,14,F"About three weeks before this
OL,15,Fhappened, this boy Skelly - Marcus
OL,16,FHuntley - and his friend came to stay
OL,17,Fat my house to sell drugs", Ms Summer
OL,18,Fsaid.
