OL,3,CDrug feuds at house days before woman
OL,4,Cshot dead, court hears
OL,6,FShe said one night, she received a
OL,7,Fcall from Huntley telling her three
OL,8,Fmen were trying to break into her flat.
OL,10,FIn the recorded police interview, Ms
OL,11,FSummers said one of the men was Daniel
OL,12,F'Jimmy' Joseph, a rival drug dealer.
OL,13,FShe said, "he'd come to the house
OL,14,Fbecause (Huntley was) selling on his
OL,15,Fturf".
OL,17,FShe told the officer that, as one of
OL,18,Fher friends helped Huntley and his
OL,19,Ffriend travel back to Cardiff, "they
OL,20,Fgot rammed off the road" by Mr Joseph.
