OL,6,F"They dumped him in my house, gave him
OL,7,F#200 worth of drugs to sell and left."
OL,9,FMs Summers said Huntley accused the
OL,10,Fboy of already stealing drugs from him
OL,11,Fand asked her to call him if he
OL,12,Ftouched any more of their supply.
OL,14,FIn the video interview shown to the
OL,15,Fcourt, Katie Summers told police on
OL,16,Fthe evening of Friday, 7th March,
OL,17,FDaniel Jospeh and two other men
OL,18,Fappeared at her front door.
