OL,6,FWhen Daniel Joseph didn't believe the
OL,7,Fman, "he pistol-whipped him across the
OL,8,Fface."
OL,10,FAs Mr Joseph left, Ms Summers says he
OL,11,Ftold her, "Tell Skelley, I want him to
OL,12,Fknow".
OL,14,FTwo days later, on Sunday, 9th March,
OL,15,FJoanne Penney was shot on the doorstep
OL,16,Fof the flat.
OL,18,FWhen asked by the police why Ms Penney
OL,19,Fwas shot, Katie Summers replied,
OL,20,F"Because of what Jimmy's done, because
OL,21,Fhe's come there with a gun.
