OL,6,F"Jimmy's turned up there with a gun,
OL,7,FI'm not sure if they thought Jimmy was
OL,8,Fgoing to be in my house then."
OL,10,F"You think the shooting is because of
OL,11,Fwhat Jimmy did?" asked the officer.
OL,12,F"Yes", she replied.
